Gamejolt Web Extractor, or also know as GWE is fully open souce, meaning that you can do your own mods, forks and anything of that sort. However it is necessary to give credits to both Sikco (The Creator and Owner of GWE) and MDT STUDIOS for inspiringy this project and such. Besides that you can do anything with this tool.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Another thing worth pointing out is that I do not condome any use of this tool for malicious intentions, I can't control how people will use this tool but I fully do not condome any use of GWE in bad ways, If you wanna extract any sort of project first get into contact with the creator of said project to get permission and information on this matter.
